            <content><![CDATA[ 
                <h2>Congratulations!</h2>
                <p>
                   Welcome to your new <a href="http://www.bigace.de/" target="_blank">Bigace</a>-powered Website.
                   This message will guide you through the first steps with Bigace.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Start by signing into Bigace with the username and password you entered during installation. 
                    To login, you can use the link located in the right sidebar.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Once signed in, visit the administration to setup your site's configuration.
                    Or you remove this message first: open the editor, replace the content and save.
                    We suggest you to explore the administration and test the various options Bigace offers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    For more about Bigace and its components please visit 
                    the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.bigace.de" title="Official BIGACE Homepage">Bigace website</a>,
                    <a target="_blank" href="http://forum.bigace.de/" title="BIGACE Forum">our forum</a> or the
                    <a target="_blank" href="http://wiki.bigace.de/" title="BIGACE Manual">Documentation</a>.
                
                </p>
                <p>
                    <i>And now have fun with your new website!</i>
                </p>
            ]]></content>
        </row>
    </table>

